<p>The <i><b>Vigiles</b></i> or more properly the <i>Vigiles Urbani</i> ("watchmen of the <a href="/wiki/Rome" title="Rome">City</a>") or <i>Cohortes Vigilum</i> ("<a href="/wiki/Cohort_(military_unit)" title="Cohort (military unit)">cohorts</a> of the watchmen") were the <a href="/wiki/Firefighter" title="Firefighter">firefighters</a> and <a href="/wiki/Police" title="Police">police</a> of <a href="/wiki/Ancient_Rome" title="Ancient Rome">Ancient Rome</a>.</p>
<p></p>
